.  SOURCE CODE FOR THE XE VERSION OF THE SIC FAMILY OF COMPUTER
.  This tests START, END, BASE, Base addressing, format 4 (ex: +LDB), Literals (ex:=C'EOF'), looping
SUM       START   0                      
FIRST     LDX    #0          
          LDA    #0          
         +LDB    #TABLE2     
          BASE    TABLE2
LOOP      ADD     TABLE,X    
          ADD     TABLE2,X   
          TIX     COUNT      
          JLT     LOOP       
         +STA     TOTAL      
          RSUB               
MYLIT    +LDA    =C'EOF'
COUNT     RESW    1
TABLE     RESW    2000
TABLE2    RESW    2000
TOTAL     RESW    1
*        =C'EOF'
          END     FIRST
